	<Title>
		Recipe: Blue cheese dressing
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Blue cheese dressing &amp;mdash; one of many healthy recipes from Mayo Clinic.
	</Abstract>
	<ServingInfo Label="Serves">
		12
	</ServingInfo>
	<DietitianTip Label="Dietitian&apos;s tip">
		&lt;p&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Dietitian&apos;s tip:&lt;/strong&gt;This tasty salad dressing comes together in the blender in no time. 
&lt;/p&gt;
	</DietitianTip>
	<Directions Label="Directions">
		&lt;p&gt;
Mix all ingredients together in a blender or food processor. Chill and serve.
&lt;/p&gt;
	</Directions>
	<Ingredients Label="Ingredients">
		&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;1/2 cup blue cheese crumbles&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;1 tablespoon minced garlic&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;1 cup fat-free mayonnaise&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;1 tablespoon horseradish&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;1 teaspoon Worcestershire sauce&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;1/2 cup low-fat buttermilk&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;1/2 teaspoon cayenne pepper&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
	</Ingredients>
